77
00:10:53,450 --> 00:10:57,060
"Eonni, you have gray hair now." That's what she would say.

78
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:09,960
Ji Yeong and Mother, they would laugh together, and worry together,

79
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:14,500
