Yeong Min.

124
00:15:49,890 --> 00:15:53,730
I hear that Yeong Min hit Joon Seo again.

125
00:15:53,730 --> 00:15:57,810
Didn't I tell you that we needed to deal with the past incident properly?

126
00:15:57,810 --> 00:16:02,850
