215
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:10,700
and what if something happens to her?

216
00:27:15,050 --> 00:27:17,250
I don't think I can live.

217
00:27:19,670 --> 00:27:22,990
I was in my right body and mind,

218
00:27:23,630 --> 00:27:26,520
