234
00:29:00,090 --> 00:29:02,390
You are so small,

235
00:29:04,380 --> 00:29:07,580
yet I just gave you such a huge burden.

236
00:29:13,180 --> 00:29:15,230
I'm sorry, Yeong Min.

237
00:29:39,020 --> 00:29:39,950
Yes?

238
